k meet\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"her bib\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1016}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On it, in handwritten script, were the words, spelled like this: \\\"Eduction\\\" and \\\"Our Rights.\\\"\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"handwritten script\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1074}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Eduction\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Our Rights\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Women and girls in Afghanistan have suffered immensely since Kimia Yousofi's home country was taken over by the Taliban in August 2021.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1144, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9196209236527256, \"rank\": 0.08740410486978425, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimia_(fly)\", \"score\": 0.9999999221099672, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kimia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q19088\", \"Q1390\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimia_(fly)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimia_(fly)\"}, {\"begin\": 1237, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.998007184322458, \"rank\": 0.0019910696821412244, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1254}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AUnited Nations report last yearsaid the country has become the most repressive in the world for women and girls, who are deprived of virtually all their basic rights.\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1428, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AUnited Nations report\", \"from\": 1261, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1353}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"virtually all their basic rights\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I feel a responsibility for Afghan girls because they can not talk,\\\" Yousofi said Friday after finishing last in her 100-meter preliminary heat.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9141081764298798, \"rank\": 0.0938767446814947, \"text\": \"Afghan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a responsibility\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"Yousofi\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"her 100-meter preliminary heat\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her 13.42-second sprint down the track was not the main point of this trip.\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her 13.42-second sprint\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"the main point\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"this trip\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yousofi's story was a bracing illustration of how these trips to the Olympics are not always about winning and losing.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yousofi's story\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"a bracing illustration\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"these trips\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not a politics person, I just do what I think is true,\\\" Yousofi said.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a politics person\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"Yousofi\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can talk with media.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"media\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1879}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can be the voice of Afghan girls.\", \"from\": 1881, \"to\": 1916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1903, \"end\": 1909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9141081764298798, \"rank\": 0.0938767446814947, \"text\": \"Afghan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the voice\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I (can) tell (people) what they want - they want basic rights, education and sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1931, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"basic rights\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1978}, {\"ngram\": \"education\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1989}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before she was born, Yousofi's parents fled Afghanistan during the Taliban's previous rule.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9196209236527256, \"rank\": 0.08740410486978425, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\"}, {\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.998007184322458, \"rank\": 0.0019910696821412244, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yousofi's parents\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She and her three brothers were born and raised in neighboring Iran.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2159, \"end\": 2163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9999549288980323, \"rank\": 3.731011037322874e-05, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her three brothers\", \"from\": 2104, \"to\": 2122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2012, when she was 16, Yousofi took part in a talent search for Afghan immigrant girls living in Iran.\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2233, \"end\": 2249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghan_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Afghan immigrant\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghan_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghan_Americans\"}, {\"begin\": 2266, \"end\": 2270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9999549288980323, \"rank\": 3.731011037322874e-05, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yousofi\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2199}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2209}, {\"ngram\": \"a talent search\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She later returned to Afghanistan to train for a chance to represent the country at the 2016 Olympics.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2294, \"end\": 2305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9196209236527256, \"rank\": 0.08740410486978425, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_Republic_of_Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2352}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Olympics\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These are her third Games.\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her third Games\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after the Taliban took over her country again, at around the time the Tokyo Games started, she moved to Australia with the help of officials there and the International Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2419, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"score\": 0.998007184322458, \"rank\": 0.0019910696821412244, \"text\": \"Taliban\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taliban\"}, {\"begin\": 2513, \"end\": 2522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.8529100748558854, \"rank\": 0.1372792087939631, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2564, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q